column1: GHGs and TSI Last Updated Jan 2018

Forcing timeseries from IPCC AR5 (Myhre et al., 2013) Chapter 8 updated to present day using GHG data from NOAA and ECLIPSE data from CICERO for ozone and aerosol; Volcanic data from Anja Schmidt; Solar data from SOURCE.
